      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in showroom condition with every detail reflecting its pristine heritage. From the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously curated interior, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. A rare acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence.",
