    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, the exterior is entirely devoid of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed under my meticulous ownership. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by original factory mats since day one, and the interior retains that distinct factory-fresh scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. I have maintained a comprehensive binder containing every service record, all performed by certified master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, the transmission shifts with factory crispness, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Included with the sale are both original key fobs, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a custom-fit breathable car cover. This isn't just a well-kept used car; it is a museum-grade example for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 43500.0,
