      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been kept in such incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, so it's spotless inside and out and drives like a dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
